    "updated_at": "2025-07-06T08:53:46Z",
    "body": "After looking how the information is retreive on starship side, it seems that the dependency [`gix`] does not support `reftable`.\n\nMy reasoning for that is the branch name is retrieve from: https://github.com/starship/starship/blob/76f125b4f593379b725b6779db65c8ff917d4bf1/src/context.rs#L832-L834\n\n(`Repository` is imported from `gix`: https://github.com/starship/starship/blob/76f125b4f593379b725b6779db65c8ff917d4bf1/src/context.rs#L10-L11)\n\nwhich is use to set the actual branch name in `get_repo`: https://github.com/starship/starship/blob/76f125b4f593379b725b6779db65c8ff917d4bf1/src/context.rs#L343\n\nWhich is used in the module `git_branch`: https://github.com/starship/starship/blob/76f125b4f593379b725b6779db65c8ff917d4bf1/src/modules/git_branch.rs#L27\n\n[`gix`]: https://docs.rs/gix/latest/gix/\n\nIt seems that they already have a tracking issue on [`gix`] side: https://github.com/GitoxideLabs/gitoxide/issues/109",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
