    "body": "Starting with Git 3.0, this backend should become the default when cloning new repositories as mentioned [here](https://lore.kernel.org/lkml/xmqqikikk1hr.fsf@gitster.g/T/#u):\n\n```\n * The reftable ref backend has matured enough; Git 3.0 will make it\n   the default format in a newly created repositories by default.\n```",
