    "body": "Even with `use_git_executable = true`, the branch is not the correct one:\n\n<img width=\"204\" height=\"64\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ed576bf2-dbea-4eb7-b25b-714f3242670b\" />\n\n<details>\n\n<summary>Starship git_status config</summary>\n\n```toml\n[git_status]\nconflicted = \"​\"\ndeleted = \"​\"\nformat = \"[[(*$conflicted$untracked$modified$staged$renamed$deleted)](218) ($ahead_behind$stashed)]($style) \"\nmodified = \"​\"\nrenamed = \"​\"\nstaged = \"​\"\nstashed = \"\"\nstyle = \"cyan\"\nuntracked = \"​\"\nuse_git_executable = true\n```\n\n</details>",
