    "body": "> yeah, I was going to say it's not working. It should be used in `git_branch` not `git_status`\n\n```\n[WARN] - (starship::config): Error in 'GitBranch' at 'use_git_executable': Unknown key \n```\n\n<details>\n\n<summary>Starship git_branch config</summary>\n\n```toml\n[git_branch]\nformat = \"[$branch]($style)\"\nstyle = \"bright-black\"\nuse_git_executable = true\n```\n\n</details>",
